Note on the base model: this repository distributes only a LoRA
adapter trained on top of Meta's Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct model. It
does not redistribute the base model's weights. Use of the base model
is subject to Meta's own Llama 3 Community License
(https://llama.meta.com/llama3/license/), independent of the CC BY-NC
